{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回「名剑香花」讲述了天下第一美男子江枫携怀孕妻子花月奴秘密出逃，在荒道上遭遇「十二星相」中的司晨客（鸡冠人）、黑面君等人的拦截抢劫。花月奴以移花宫墨玉梅花震慑贼人，短暂脱险后动了胎气，在马车中产下一对双胞胎男婴。十二星相去而复返，发现花月奴不过是移花宫逃出的宫女而非真正的移花宫主，遂痛下杀手。江枫拼死护妻，身负重伤，花月奴以移花接玉击退敌人，但二人终因伤势过重而奄奄一息，场面凄惨悲壮。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "没有什么，只不过走错路了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "你又走错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "你又何苦瞒我？我早已知道了。",
      "tone": "轻叹",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "你早已知道了？",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "我方才听见那声鸡啼，便已猜出必定是「十二星相」中人找上咱们了，你怕我担心，所以才瞒着我，是么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "奇怪……你我此行如此秘密，他们怎会知道？但……但你只管放心，什么事都有我来抵挡！",
      "tone": "长叹",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "你又错了，自从那天……那天我准备和你共生共死，无论有什么危险患难，也该由咱们俩共同承当。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "但你现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "没关系，现在我觉得很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "好，你还能下车走么？道路两头都已有警兆，看来咱们也只有弃下车马，穿过这一片荒野……",
      "tone": "咬牙",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "为什么要弃下车马呢？他们既已盯上咱们，反正已难脱身，倒不如就在这里等着，「十二星相」虽然有凶名，但咱们也未必怕他们！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "我……我只是怕你……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "你放心，我没关系。",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "我能找着你，真是最幸运的事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "幸运的该是我才对，我知道，江湖中不知道有多少女孩子在羡慕我，妒忌我，只是她们……",
      "tone": "笑意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们似已来了！",
      "tone": "变色",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "不错，咱们已来了！",
      "tone": "嗄嗄笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？！",
      "tone": "大惊",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "来的可是「十二星相」中之司晨客与黑面君么？",
      "tone": "强作镇定",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "江公子果然好眼力，但咱们不过是一只鸡、一只猪而已，司晨客、黑面君，这些好听的名字，不过是江湖中人胡乱取的，咱们承当不起。",
      "tone": "咯咯笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "阁下想必就是……",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "红的是鸡冠，黄的是鸡胸，花的是鸡尾，至于后面那位，你瞧他模样像什么，他就是什么。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "几位不知有何见教？",
      "tone": "客气",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "闻得江公子有了新宠，咱兄弟都忍不住想来瞧瞧这位能令玉郎动心的美人儿究竟美到什么地步，再者，咱兄弟还想来向公子讨件东西。",
      "tone": "直接",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "只可惜在下此次匆匆出门，身无长物，哪有什么好东西，能人得了诸位名家法眼。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "江公子此刻突然将家财完全变卖，咱们虽不知为的是什么，却也不想知道，但江公子以田庄换来的那袋明珠……嘿嘿，江公子也该知道咱们「十二星相」向来贼不空手，公子就把那袋明珠赏给咱们吧。",
      "tone": "嗄嗄笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "好，好，原来你们倒竟已打听得如此清楚，在下也知道「十二星相」从来不轻易出手，出手后从不空回，但……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "但什么？你不答应？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "若要我答应，只有……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "哥儿们，加加油，咱们可不是女人，可莫要对这小子生出怜香惜玉的心，兄弟我且先去瞧瞧车子里的小美人儿。",
      "tone": "嘻嘻笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "怒喝",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "你们瞧瞧这是什么？",
      "tone": "一字字缓缓",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "绣玉谷，移花宫。",
      "tone": "嗄声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "你的眼力倒也不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "我……小人。",
      "tone": "结巴",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "你们想不想死？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "小人，不……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "不想死的还不走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "你……你没事么？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "我只不过招了招手而已。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "不想你竟从宫中带出了朵墨玉梅花，连「十二星相」这样的凶人，竟也对她们如此惧怕。",
      "tone": "叹",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "由此你就可想到她们有多可怕，咱们还是快走吧，别的人来了都不要紧，但若是……",
      "tone": "忧虑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "咱们险些上当了，车子里若真是「移花宫」中的人，方才还能活着走么？你几时听说过「移花宫」手下留得有活口？",
      "tone": "哈哈大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "我饶了你，你竟还……",
      "tone": "气愤",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "冒牌货，出来吧！",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "原来是个大肚婆娘，居然还敢冒充移花宫的……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "这大肚婆如何？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "暗算偷袭，又算得什么？",
      "tone": "怒吼",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "移花接玉，神鬼莫敌……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "你既然知道，便也该知道我是不是冒充的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "小……小人该死、该死……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "我要为孩子积点阴德，你们……你们快走吧。",
      "tone": "叹",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "你怎么了？",
      "tone": "大惊",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "我……我动了胎气……只怕……只怕已……快要……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "这如何是好？",
      "tone": "慌乱",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "你快将车子赶到路旁……快……快……快！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两个……是双胞胎……",
      "tone": "狂喜",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "你……你们又回来了？",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "公子吃惊了么？",
      "tone": "诡笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "你们莫非要来送死不成？！",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "姓江的，你还装什么蒜？你知道，我也知道，移花宫两位宫主，此刻想要的是你们两人的命，可不是我们。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "我瞧你倒真是疯子，移花宫的宫主会想要我的命？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "鸡冠人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "现在车子里的，不过是移花宫的宫女、丫头，只不过是自移花宫逃出来的叛徒！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "江公子又吃惊了吧？江公子只怕还要问，这种事咱们又怎会知道？嘿嘿，这可是件秘密，你可永远也猜不到。",
      "tone": "哈哈大笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_ji_guan_ren",
      "text": "留神！这小子拼上命了！",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_jiang_feng",
      "text": "玉郎，你小心些……只要你小心些，他们绝不是你的敌手！",
      "tone": "呻吟着呼",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "唷，这小子确气不错，居然还是个双胞胎！",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "江枫",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "恶贼，滚开！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "花月奴",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "text": "恶贼，你……你……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_jun",
      "speaker_name": "黑面君",
      "listener": "char_hua_yue_nu",
      "text": "小美人儿，你放心，现在我不会对你怎样的，但等你好了，我却要……哈哈，哈哈……",
